protocol_info.protocol_name: A Phase III, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of NovaPlex-450 in Combination with Standard Chemotherapy in Patients with Advanced Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer
protocol_info.primary_objective: To evaluate progression-free survival (PFS) in patients treated with NovaPlex-450 plus chemotherapy versus placebo plus chemotherapy
